root_school_name_A: j~nanajyoti im vo skula putalibajara sya~naja
bhavani prasada sakala prasada rama prasada janata
phaychara stara i vo skula sya~naja
ne ra pra sharada skula palpa
bhagavati ne ra vagad maina yadava
shahida jagata pra ja sha sam
bhagavati shikshaka seva ayoga naumule ga pa dailekha
ne ra pra je pi chaturvedi
ne ra pra avi pakadiya parsa
maisthana bala vidya mandira indu lakhe
ne ra lakshmana saha chandra jyoti
a ra pra yu va semarakhora kapilabastu
ramajanaki rama krrishna dasa yu ma
j~nanajyoti laduvati deva na yadava rashtriya
shri bada maharani ratna rajya lakshmi kanya
maristhana bala vidya mandira indu lakhe
sarasvati uchch ma go na pa
shri pam ramadeni tivari ne ra
shahida ka ra ra sim bha ra vi
rashtriya pustakalaya va su purva navalaparasi
maisthana bala vidya mandira indu lakhe
rama janaki tinadhara pathashala lakshmipura sukhachaina sarlahi
